{
  "stem": "27129.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't give it a thought, because they kept writing in the papers that England-- England, which was a big power at that time, and France, you know, those two big powers, they will fight back, you know, in the case, you know, if war breaks out, and blah, blah, blah.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so, you know, people are people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They read the paper and they think this is what-- what is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When war broke out, until we got to know, you know, what's happening in the 6th of September, 1939, they broadcast over the radio that all people that were of military age-- and I was already close to it, but my two brothers were already of military age-- they should take a little food, you know, and a little belongings and go out of the city.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's going to happen there, nobody knew, but we thought, you know, maybe they're going to induct them into the army and they're going to fight back the Germans.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in the meantime, what happened is that I-- I went with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we left my mother, you know, alone, because my mother said, well, maybe it's better-- for the better, you know, that you go out and then you come back when everything was-- will quiet down, you know?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People thought that this is just a matter of a-- a few days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when we came out of the city, walking obviously, we didn't have nothing-- we didn't have no cars or horses-- we saw a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were running, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The military were-- were running, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Polish military?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Polish military.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were stepping back, you know, from the Germans, pushed them back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you had civil-- civilian people, you know, a mix-up.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
